data.description: LARGE LOT, RV PARKING, NO HOA, & IMPROVEMENT POTENTIAL!! This charming Single-Family Home is the perfect starter home.  Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious open floor plan, perfect for entertaining family and friends. Boasting two bedrooms and two bathrooms, this home is perfect for anyone looking for a cozy, yet comfortable living space. A two-car attached garage is an added bonus, providing ample space for parking and storage.    The primary bedroom features plush carpeted flooring and a walk-in closet. The second bedrooms also boasts a walk-in closet! The living room is bright and airy, with large windows that let in plenty of natural light. The kitchen has beautiful wooden cabinets, perfect for a home chef, and the bathroom features a double sink and glass door.    This home is ready for your personal touch, with endless opportunities for home improvement and upgrades. With an RV parking space and a private backyard, there's plenty of room for outdoor activities, making it the perfect choice for families.    Located in a quiet neighborhood with sidewalks and street parking, this home is conveniently situated near restaurants and amenities. Within a 15-minute drive, you'll find De Anza Elementary School and Mount San Jacinto College, as well as healthcare options, including Rite Aid and CVS Pharmacy.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this lovely single-family home your own. Schedule a viewing today and start creating memories in your new home!
